J.M. and T.B., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D19-1716 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 08, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioners' petition for writ of prohibition is denied. Petitioners' "Motion to Supplement Record" is denied.

LaROSE, C.J., and CASANUEVA and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
